external_references.description: Secureworks Counter Threat Unit Research Team. (2022, August 17). DarkTortilla Malware Analysis. Retrieved November 3, 2022.

objects.description: [DarkTortilla](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S1066) can download additional packages for keylogging, cryptocurrency mining, and other capabilities; it can also retrieve malicious payloads such as [Agent Tesla](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0331), AsyncRat, [NanoCore](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0336), RedLine, [Cobalt Strike](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0154), and Metasploit.(Citation: Secureworks DarkTortilla Aug 2022)
